"Kevin Slavin is Managing Director and Co-Founder of area/code. He is one of the inventors of '''Big Games, which are large-scale, real-world games.'''


A Big Game might involve transforming an entire city into the world's largest board game, or hundreds of players scouring the streets looking for invisible treasure, or a TV show reaching out to interact with real-time audiences nationwide."


